<L><PB N="42" REF="50">
Pen&s;ive &s;he walks to take the Evening Air,</L>
<L>At her Approach, the Greens fre&s;h Verdure wear;</L>
<L>For her Companion, flowing <HI>Horace</HI> cho&s;e,</L>
