<L><PB N="43" REF="51">
Dear Nymph! you &s;eem the Godde&s;s of this Grove;</L>
<L>Or, what is more, th' Immortal Queen of Love!</L>
<L>Let that &s;oft Form, a tender Heart contain,</L>
